content: Solar Panel Wiring May Melt Causing Fire

Forest River, Inc. (Forest River) is recalling certain 2025 Coachmen Apex and Remote travel trailers.  The solar panel wiring may be incorrectly wired to the battery, causing it to melt.Melted wiring may cause an electrical short, increasing the risk of a fire.

Number of Units Affected: 69.0
